                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 19.727,
                                "byte_start": 77462,
                                "byte_stop": 156456,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion in Number 80-427, Fair Assessment in Real Estate Association against McNary and 80-1377, Weinberger against the Catholic Action of Hawaii will each be announced by Justice Rehnquist."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 19.727,
                        "stop": 211.668,
